data.description: Stunning open-concept floor plan, this well crafted log home is breathtaking. Large windows bathe the space with natural light. Expansive pine flanked rooms create uninterrupted ambiance. Warmth emanated by the stone fireplace/stove sets the tone for peace & calm. Exposed beams, natural materials, gorgeous tones. The large kitchen with plenty of cabinetry space & breakfast bar opens to the dining area. The inviting primary bedroom with walk in closet is set off from the main living area. Upper level offers oversized loft area & is perfect for home office/home entertainment space, peaceful retreat.  2nd br/ba are also upper level. Large basement opens to outside by 2 lift doors & pedestrian door. Basement doubles as 2-car garage. Laundry hook ups. Plenty of space for workshop/storage. Enjoy all seasons on the wrap-around porch overlooking the serene countryside. Tend your flock in the chicken coop with run. May be divided with county approval. Close to Monroe, Hwy74 Bypass to Charlotte.
